channel.title: Cache Error
channel.description:
I made some changes in my client. After I made those changes, I compiled them. I got this error: [code=smarty]client.java:3259: cannot find symbol symbol : class Update location: class client new Update("(Cache LINK)", "cache.zip", signlink.findcachedir(), true, true) ; ^ Note: Some input files use or override a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. 1 error Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
There actually is a cache link there but I didn't put it there cuz I think Advertising isn't aloud. :P
I tried to make a few changes to the link but it didn't work
